Lumpy skin disease, Saudi Arabia
--------------------------------
Information received on [and dated] 14 Jul 2016 from Dr Mohammed Alblowi, Director General, Diagnostic Veterinary Laboratories, Ministry of Agriculture, Riyadh, Saudi Arabia

Summary
Report type: Immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 16 Apr 2016
Date of confirmation of the event: 5 Jun 2016
Reason for notification: Reoccurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence: 10 Jul 2015
Manifestation of disease: Clinical disease
Causal agent: Lumpy skin disease virus
Nature of diagnosis: Laboratory (advanced)
This event pertains to the whole country

