Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: Unknown or inconclusive

Control measures
Measures applied: Movement control inside the country; vaccination in response to the outbreak(s); disinfection/disinfestation; control of vectors; no treatment of affected animals.
Measures to be applied: No other measures

Diagnostic test results
Laboratory name and type / Species / Test / Test date / Result
Alhsa Veterinary Laboratory (national laboratory) / Cattle / real-time (PCR) / 5 Jun 2016 / Positive

Future reporting
The event is continuing. Weekly follow-up reports will be submitted.

